                            "game-obj": "Traits",
                            "aonid": 623
                        }
                    }
                ],
                "text": "When the leshy dies, a burst of primal energy explodes from their body, restoring Hit Points based on the leshy's level to each plant creature in a 30-foot emanation. This area is filled with plants, becoming difficult terrain. If the terrain is not a viable environment for these plants, they wither after 24 hours.",
